# pivotai Fine-Tuned Model
# Run from project root: ollama create pivotai-ft -f phase3_training/notebooks/modelfiles/Modelfile.ft
FROM ../../../models/finetune/pivotai_ft.gguf

PARAMETER temperature 0.3
PARAMETER top_p 0.9
PARAMETER top_k 40
PARAMETER repeat_penalty 1.1
PARAMETER num_predict 16384
PARAMETER stop "<|eot_id|>"
PARAMETER stop "### Instruction:"

SYSTEM """You are pivotai Optimizer, an AI travel assistant for Indian domestic trips.
Given a traveler persona (JSON), produce an optimized day-by-day itinerary that minimizes cost while respecting the budget tier, trip type, and traveler intents.
Identify the primary Price-Pivot Point (transit, accommodation, or activity substitution that saves ≥5%) and explain it clearly.
Always respond with valid JSON containing 'optimized' itinerary and 'pivot_analysis'."""
